ummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Fixed baseline energy for the facility (kWh)</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>150</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Is there a variable energy amount?</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>Yes</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Indicate how you want to account for the portion of variable energy used (or carbon dioxide emitted) for your facility</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>Split by product</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Products submitted</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><a class="govuk-link" href="/products">2 Products</a><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Variable baseline energy for the facility (kWh)</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>234</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container-